{"tid":1375991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"策略討論  吹雞叫罷工既巴打請入","createTime":"2019-07-28T08:07:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T12:38:06.000Z","uid":17510,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"422f6fc711a83390a4bc2ce10313eac169c80a7a","tid":1375991,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T08:07:59.000Z","msg":"我想講時至今日有好多打工仔依然無心去罷工<br />\n我地要反思下點想去說服佢地<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>問題:</strong><br />\n<strong>宣傳不足</strong><br />\n我地一直都淨係連登宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係有啲人都會上連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係真係佔極少數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>香港打工仔真係好國際化</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多超級巨型跨國企業香港亞太總部，員工組成比例如下<br />\n30% 鬼佬<br />\n鬼佬其實支持我地，不過心態係你唔好阻到佢返工就得。之前我地地鐵不合作運動好無謂，完全都威脅唔到港共、影響唔到商業機構、影響唔到地鐵營利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即係我地行動目的未夠準確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n30% 中国人<br />\n移民到港支那人，除左中聯辦同港澳辦，其實好多都支持我地，佢地心態同鬼佬差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實依班人當中有唔少都係覺得香港好過共匪黨先黎香港。所以佢地精神上好支持我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我覺得只要同依班人好好交流，佢地絕對有機會成為我地既生力軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n20% 香港人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好多時香港人都係好低層既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />根本話唔到事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好多國際公司無左你唔會停止運作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本地公司又唔夠力量去造力壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n認真，你地淨連登宣傳有乜用？得幾丁友有上連登，一石未必能擊起千重浪。<br />\n我地怪責做乜嘢人地唔響影罷工，<br />\n我地亦要理解一點<br />\n<strong>有上連登既打工仔未必係高層<br />\n係高層上左年紀既人士又未必識上連登</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>對策</strong><br />\n<strong>化整為零攻略上班一族</strong><br />\n係放工時間我的確見過有巴打係街頭宣傳遊行<br />\n但係大家有無諗過係lunch hour或者放工時段要去核心商業區宣傳？<br />\n你既宣傳對象應該要包括在港既鬼佬同中国人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n宣傳唔係話你整個大聲公出黎講人自講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而係要試下engage依班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同佢地傾下睇下佢地有乜諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />試下去說服佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁樣先係真真正正既宣傳罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你要明白<strong>真正決定香港命脈既人</strong>從來都唔係香港人自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而<strong>係依一班國際巨企既管理人員</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a36122359c8185e8cbcfe471460839c2d317c37","tid":1375991,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T08:10:33.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"3afe8f0a87e92a808ba794436c8f24abb87608ac","tid":1375991,"uid":29167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T08:10:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1375822/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1375822/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[728] 需要地方落腳嘅手足